{
  "chapter": 16,
  "chapter_summary": "楚留香与黑珍珠约定在大明湖以黑马引路相见后，返回丐帮香堂。南宫灵早已备酒等候，妙僧无花亲自下厨素斋相待，三人把酒夜谈。席间楚留香试探南宫灵关于沙漠之王札木合的死讯，南宫灵故作不知。楚留香追问任老帮主夫人的下落，南宫灵最终答应带路前往尼山。楚留香先行离去，在大明湖畔寻到黑珍珠，托付其转告等候一位苏姓少女。随后楚留香与南宫灵同赴曲阜尼山，一路谈论任老帮主生前往事与江湖疾苦，渐近任夫人隐居之所。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "明天早上……若是我知道在什么地方能找着你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "明天早上，你到大明湖边逛一圈，就会瞧见一匹黑色的马，你对它说三声带我去见黑珍珠，将它的左耳拉三下，它就会送你去找我的，记着，不多不少，只能拉三下，不能太轻，更不能太重。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "我若拉了四下，又拉重了呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那么它只怕就要送你去寻真的珍珠了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黑珍珠呀黑珍珠，别人常说黑色不祥，但愿你这黑珍珠能带给我些运气才好，我现在实在太需要运气了……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "南宫兄可在?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gai_bang_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "丐帮弟子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "请进。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "楚兄果然来讨酒债了，幸好小弟早已备下几瓶酒，否则楚兄来到这里，小弟只有逃之夭夭了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "你知道我能找得到这里?你一点儿也不奇怪?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "楚兄若要讨酒债时，天下有谁能逃得掉?小弟就算已躲到天边，楚兄寻着，也是毫不稀奇的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "不错，我这鼻子素来有点毛病，哪里有好酒，我一嗅就嗅出来了，何况是这么多瓶上好的竹叶青。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "只可惜有酒无菜，未免美中不足，你可知道，这对我这好吃之徒来说，简直是虐待。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "菜本来有的，小弟备得有几只肥鸡，一只猪蹄，还有些熏鱼腊肉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "鸡鱼腊肉莫非也会隐身法不成，我怎地瞧不见?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "楚兄瞧不见，只因方才有个人来，已将菜都倒在阴沟里去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "这人难道与我有什么深仇大恨不成?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他知道小弟等的客人是楚兄，便将小弟责骂了一顿，说小弟以这样的粗菜来款待楚兄，未免太虐待楚香帅的舌头了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "楚留香不吃鸡肉，难道只喝西北风不成?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "红尘劳苦，已令世人之灵性所剩无几，若再将那样的肥鸡肥肉吃下去，仅存的灵性只怕也要被蒙住了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_wu_hua",
      "text": "原来是你，你这妙僧不沾荤腥，难道要我也学你做和尚不成?何况我就算做了和尚，也是酒肉和尚，见了大鱼大肉，立刻就要动凡心的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "食肉者鄙，难道你不想换换口味?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_wu_hua",
      "text": "莫非你竟肯下厨房了?",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "抚琴需有知音，美味也得要知味者才能品尝，若非为了你这从小就培养得能分辨好坏滋味的舌头，贫僧又何苦沾这一身烟火气。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_wu_hua",
      "text": "你若也有烟火气，那咱们岂非是从锅里捞出来了么?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这倒也奇怪，无花大师无论从什么地方走出来，看来都要比我等干净十倍，凡世中的尘垢，似乎都染不到他，天女散花，维摩不染，只怕也正是此意吧!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "幸好酒之一物，其质最纯，否则大师若连酒都不喝了，我等情何以堪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_wu_hua",
      "text": "若是三人饮酒，惟你不醉，我才是真的佩服你了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "据闻江湖中还有一人，酒量号称无敌，能饮千杯不醉，有一日连喝了三百碗关外二锅头，居然还能站着走回去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "哦，有这样的人?是谁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "便是那人称沙漠之王的札木合。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "说是三百碗，其实若有半数，也就不错了，天下喝酒的人，没有一个不将自己的酒量夸大几分，以小弟看来，他也未必喝得过你我。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "你可曾见过他?可曾与他同席饮酒?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "可惜小弟未曾见过他，否则倒真要和他拼个高低。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这机会恐怕不多了。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "只要他未死，日后总有机会的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "谁说他未死?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他已死了么?何时死的?江湖中为何无人知道?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "你怎知道江湖中没有人知道他的死讯?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "丐帮消息最是灵通，江湖中若已有人知道这消息，丐帮的帮主还会不知道么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "不错，江湖中的确还没有人知道这消息，只因我已藏起了他的尸身，故意不要别人知道他的死讯。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀死他的人，故布疑阵，要使江湖中人以为他们乃是互相火并而死，而且都已死光了，我若不藏起他们的尸身，而将这消息透露，那真凶便可逍遥法外，我为何要让他如此安逸?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，楚兄这样做，他们的门人亲属既不知道他们已死，想必要拼命追查他们的下落，那真凶自然也休想过得了太平门子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "贫僧早已说过，恶徒遇着楚香帅，想是前生造孽太多了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "你可愿助我寻出那真凶来?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "楚兄莫忘了，丐帮弟子爱管闲事的名声，纵在楚香帅之下，却也是差不了许多的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "如此便请你告诉我，任老帮主的夫人，此刻在哪里?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "任夫人难道也与此事有关系?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "内中隐情，你日后自会知道，现在你只要说出任夫人在哪里，就等于帮了我一个最大的忙了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "你若不肯说，只怕我便要认为你是在有意藏匿真凶，我若胡说八道起来，你这丐帮帮主只怕也是受不了的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "楚兄最可爱之处，便是有时他会像孩子般撒赖。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "任老帮主故去后，任夫人发愿守节，小弟身为丐帮子弟，本不能带领外人去惊扰于她。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但小弟别人不怕，见了楚兄却是无可奈何的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "你答应了?",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那藏匿真凶的罪名，小弟怎担当得起?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "任夫人现在哪里?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "任夫人居处甚是隐秘，旁人也难以寻着，楚兄若肯将这剩下的大半瓶酒都喝下去，小弟就带楚兄走一趟如何?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "你要难他一难，就该另外出个主意才是，要他喝酒，岂非正中他下怀。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_wu_hua",
      "text": "到底是无花知我。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "现在可以走了吧?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "楚兄不知可否再等一个时辰，小弟帮中还有些琐事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "咱们的去处，两天内能赶回来么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "两天只怕已够了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "楚兄如此急着赶回，莫非佳人有约?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_wu_hua",
      "text": "别人常说什么事都瞒不过我，我看这句话却该转赠于你才是。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "月下大明湖，人约黄昏后，楚兄这样的人，到了济南府而没有一两件这样的风流韵事，那才真有些奇怪了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "好，我一个多时辰后，再来找你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无花好菜，南宫好酒，来了就吃，吃了就走，人生如此，夫复何求，酒足饭饱，快乐无俦。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "楚留香，好快的手。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若非无足轻重之物，贫僧怎会让他取去，他若肯稍敛锋芒，莫要炫露，只怕就会活得长久些。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "马儿呀马儿，只可惜你是我朋友所有之物，否则我真舍不得让别人骑在你的背上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "text": "你在想什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我在想你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "想你是否已问出来了?",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "text": "还未问出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我早就知道他不会告诉你的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "text": "他虽未告诉我，但却要带我去了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "好，你们在前面走，我在后面跟着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "text": "你若想在后面跟着南宫灵，而不被他发现，轻功只怕还不够。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "纵然被他发觉，他又能将我怎样?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "text": "也没有怎样，只不过你我再也休想寻着任夫人了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你要去多久?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "text": "两天。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "好，两天后，我还是在这里等你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "text": "两天后，黄昏时，有个身穿淡色衣衫的少女，会到大明湖来，那时我若尚未赶回，就请你告诉她，要她等等我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "佳人有约黄昏后，楚留香倒果然风流得很，只可惜我又不认得你那位佳人，又怎么代你转告?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "text": "她姓苏，你一见着她，就会知道的，大明湖纵然地灵人杰，但像她那样的女孩子也不会太多。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她很美?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "text": "单这美之一字，又怎能形容她?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她是你的什么人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "text": "你不觉问得太多了么?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "好，你去吧……但她若不肯等你又如何?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "text": "她若不肯等我，我就跳下这大明湖去淹死。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你倒自信得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "text": "若刨去自信，楚留香能剩下的，只怕已不过是滩臭水罢了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "text": "你不觉得你这名字有些像女人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我若是女人，只怕早已宰了你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "text": "你若是女人，只怕就不会对我这么凶了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "咱们离开济南已有多久?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "才不过一天，你难道忘了?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "我虽然刚到这里，但想起济南城里那些凡俗纷争，就已像上辈子的事了，若在这里长住下去，我这俗人只怕也要变为雅士。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "任老帮主生前，就总是想到这里来结庐隐居，他常说这里有匡庐之幽绝，而无匡庐之游客，有黄山之灵秀，而无黄山之虚名，只可惜他一生忙碌，这志愿竟只有等到他死后才能实现。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "你很想念他?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他是我一生中所见过最仁慈，最和蔼的人，我……我本是个孤儿，没有他，也就没有今天。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "我与你相识多年，这些话，倒是第一次听你说起。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "江湖之中，强存弱亡，竞争之剧，无一日一时或休，有些事，我既无时间去想，也不敢去想它。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "不错，有些事若是想得太多，心就会改变的，而心肠太软的人，也的确无法在江湖中生存下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "任夫人莫非住在山巅?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "任夫人风华绝代，举世无双，又怎甘居于人下?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "我这人从来不大容易紧张的，但想到别人说过的有关任夫人之种种风流韵事，再想到自己立刻就要见着她了，一颗心竟也不觉跳了起来。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    }
  ],
